  "text": "Medical morbidity was assessed using the Self-Administered Comorbidity Questionnaire (SCQ). [CITATION_1] In this study, we counted the number of conditions that, according to caregivers, limited either participant or caregiver activities, with total possible scores ranging from 0 to 15.",
